Welcome to the worlds of Warhammer and to a fun hobby of collecting, painting and playing games with Warhammer fantasy miniatures. At Games Workshop Birmingham,AL we have everything you need to begin, or grow, your collection and our friendly manager will be delighted to help you choose the right miniatures, paints and accessories for you. Will you choose Warhammer Age of Sigmar, a time when heroes, gods, and monsters fight a desperate battle for the fate of the Mortal Realms? Or Warhammer 40,000, where in the grim darkness of the far future, mankind battles in an unending war of incredible heroism and bitter betrayal? The choice is yours! Located at 1717 Montgomery Hwy, Birmingham,AL we offer free introductory activities and have friendly and approachable staff who will be delighted to help chose the right model for you or assist you with all your gift-buying needs.
